Transcript:
Agent: Hello, main Aryan hoon Trimfinity se. Maine dekha ki aapne product cart mein add kiya tha. Aaj ke din aapke liye additional 5% off hai. Kya aap ise claim karna chahenge?
User: Yes.
Agent: Wah, badhiya! Aapne bilkul sahi decision liya hai. Main aapko abhi ek WhatsApp link bhejta hoon jisme aapko checkout karne ka option milega. Bas uspe click karke payment complete kar lijiye aur aapka Trimfinity 7000 Pro Max Body & Ball Trimmer jaldi aapke paas hoga.

Aur haan, aapko 5% ka discount code bhi de raha hoon—O-F-F-5. Isse apply karna mat bhooliyega!

Agar aapko koi bhi dikkat ho, toh humein call kar sakte hain: seven-three-nine-seven-eight-zero-five-three-four-seven.
Agent: Hello ji, lagta hai aap thoda busy ho gaye. Koi baat nahi, main aapko WhatsApp pe checkout link bhej raha hoon aur discount code bhi yaad rakhiyega—O-F-F-5. Aap jab free ho, tab checkout kar lena.

Agar koi bhi sawal ya dikkat ho, toh mujhe zarur batana. Hum hamesha madad ke liye ready hain!
CallSummary: The agent informed the user about a 5% discount on a product they added to their cart and offered to send a WhatsApp link for checkout. The user accepted the offer, and the agent provided a discount code and reassured the user that they could reach out for assistance if needed.
